過分倚重美斯，今屆幾乎又由他一手率球隊從外圍賽突圍、只要在場就幾乎參與每個攻勢，到了大賽，如此最容易被針對性部署。既然現任主帥森柏奧利曾率智利打敗阿根廷，打敗了美斯，肯定明白集體力量勝於一切。美斯想圓夢，最好不要再站在前線，墮後誘敵並為隊友穿針引線才是最明智，是一種昇華。<br />\n<br />\n單天保至尊難成大業，成王還得靠隊友。一次又一次嘗過「二奶」苦水，如果美斯從中明白自己退一格，球隊可能進一步，當不見得德國、巴西等勁敵實力明顯比4年前強多少，且各有隱憂，7‧15也許就是美斯圓夢之日。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n文：藍鑽石"},{"pid":"4a0ab2df5e2814d47c3c6cff9ba2a8d82a26b3c7","tid":704824,"uid":17752,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T16:31:06.000Z","msg":"C朗可以和波和到攞歐國冠軍 我肥斯一樣得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb01fcbf7531289288caeecd82ac3d37e7fbdfd","tid":704824,"uid":166434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T16:53:56.000Z","msg":"唔學埋人地分組賽入波 ？"},{"pid":"11da748ca242bac5e3cc65ef257e1e23536dc8cb","tid":704824,"uid":166434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71402b93c0bfe8471448dc06c701150161be4ae4","tid":704824,"uid":141879,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"26c82a90072e426f24445497e245833471951b7f","tid":704824,"uid":11254,"like":99,"dislike":0,"score":99,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T15:50:42.000Z","msg":"係呀 但第三係出局"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T15:53:27.000Z","msg":"咁咪避晒強對囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T16:54:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b94c79144e434e63ce35b63cb6cf7f757bc761c3","tid":704824,"uid":11173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2eb01fcbf7531289288caeecd82ac3d37e7fbdfd","tid":704824,"uid":166434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T16:53:56.000Z","msg":"唔學埋人地分組賽入波 ？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T17:00:06.000Z","msg":"今場模仿射失十二碼，第三場就爆seed熱血迫和<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgm